{% extends 'base.html.twig' %}

{% block content %}
    <div class="container">

        <div class="row">
            <div class="box">
                <div class="col-lg-12">
                    <hr>
                    <h2 class="intro-text text-center text-uppercase">Hi-Math
                        <br>A brighter tomorrow, together.</h2>
                    <hr>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-8 text-content">
                    <p>With the pace that the technology is moving forward, one has to be creative to stay ahead. Hi-Math has made its mission to help equip the younger generation with tools and knowledge to gear their education toward the real-world demands especially in the IT field.</p>
                    <hr>

                    <p>Children, starting from their high school years, benefit from the innovative educational programs that Hi-Math helps bring to life. Getting trained in state-of-the-art technologies while gaining exposure to the demands of the leading IT firms is one of the ways to prepare a generation that is ready to take on the tasks of the future.
                    </p>
                    <hr>
                    <p>
                        Here is an opportunity for you to play your own role in helping this effort. Your donation of any size will make a difference. To make an even bigger impact, please consider to become an ongoing sponsor by subscribing to monthly donations of any amount of your choice. Please click the button below to peruse either option of your choice.
                    </p>
                    <div class="col-lg-12 col-md-12 text-center">
                        <form action="https://www.paypal.com/cgi-bin/webscr" method="post" target="_top">
                            <input type="hidden" name="cmd" value="_s-xclick">
                            <input type="hidden" name="hosted_button_id" value="RUVWW4KVU54XJ">
                            <input type="image" src="https://www.paypalobjects.com/en_US/i/btn/btn_donateCC_LG.gif"
                                   border="0" name="submit" alt="PayPal - The safer, easier way to pay online!">
                            <img alt="" border="0" src="https://www.paypalobjects.com/en_US/i/scr/pixel.gif" width="1"
                                 height="1" draggable="false">
                        </form>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <form class="form-inline text-center">
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label class="sr-only" for="exampleInputAmount">Amount (in dollars)</label>
                            <div class="input-group">
                                <a href="#" class="input-group-addon"><i class="icon-search"></i></a>
                                <input type="text" class="form-control" id="exampleInputAmount" placeholder="Search">
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </form>

                    <h3 class="brand-name text-center" style="font-size: 28px; margin-top: 20px">Recent Posts</h3>
                    <hr class="tagline-divider">
                    <a href="#"><p class="text-center text-uppercase" style="font-size: 20px">
                            FIND YOUR INNER POWER BY HELPING OTHERS
                        </p>
                    </a>
                    <hr class="tagline-divider">
                    <div class="col-md-12">
                        <div id="example1"></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="clearfix"></div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <!-- /.container -->
{% endblock %}
